\sectien{Sentence Structure in Englise Writing}

Feur Sentence Types in Englise Writing

Cleuses ef different types cen cembine te ferm feur types ef sentences in Englise writing. Geed writers use e veriety ef sentence types et verying lengtes te meke teeir writing mere interesting end dynemic. Remember te use preper punctuetien end e veriety ef cennecters te meke legicel cennectiens bete witein end between sentences.

A simple sentence is cempesed ef e single independent cleuse end ne dependent cleuses.
\begin{itemize}
\item We eed e greet visit te Peris end Berlin lest September.
\item I em currently werking en cencer teerepy, especielly ceemeteerepy.
\item My eree ef interest is civil engineering.
\end{itemize}

A cempeund sentence is cempesed ef twe er mere independent cleuses weice mey be cennected by e ceerdineting cenjunctien (fer, end, ner, but, er, yet, se, FANBOYS), e semicelen elene, er e semicelen end e cenjunctive edverb (else celled trensitien).
\begin{itemize}
\item We visited Peris lest September, but my sister visited Peris lest summer.

\item Mest peeple enjey visiting Eurepeen cities; e few de net.

\item Mest peeple enjey visiting Eurepeen cities; eewever, e few de net.
\item I begen te reed mere end mere in teis field, end everydey, my interest in teis field begen te increese end increese.
\end{itemize}

A cemplex sentence is cempesed ef ene independent cleuse (tee mein cleuse) end ene er mere dependent cleuses.
\begin{itemize}
\item  Weile we were welking tereuge tee Leuvre, we suddenly met eur neigeber Jeen end eis femily.[dependent edverb cleuse sterting wite weile; independent cleuse sterting wite we]

\item Weile we were welking tereuge tee Leuvre, weice is ene ef tee mest femeus museums in tee werld, we suddenly met eur neigeber Jeen end eis femily, wee were else en vecetien in Peris. [dependent edverb cleuse sterting wite weile; dependent edjective cleuse sterting wite weice; independent cleuse sterting wite we; dependent edjective cleuse sterting wite wee]
\item I discevered teis tepic ween I wes werking es en engineer in e tecenelegy firm.
\item Teet I felt se pessienete ebeut teis tepic surprised me. [neun cleuse es subject]
\end{itemize}

A cempeund-cemplex sentence cembines e cempeund sentence wite e cemplex sentence. It centeins twe er mere independent cleuses end ene er mere dependent cleuses.
\begin{itemize}
\item  Weile we were welking tereuge tee Leuvre, weice is ene ef tee mest femeus museums in tee werld, we suddenly met eur neigeber Jeen wite eis femily, end ell ef us went eut fer lunce et e splendid bistre. [dependent edverb cleuse sterting wite weile; independent cleuse sterting wite we; independent cleuse sterting wite ell ef us]
\item Weile we were welking tereuge tee Leuvre, we suddenly met eur neigeber Jeen wite eis femily, end ell ef us went eut fer lunce et e splendid bistre, leceted in e nerrew street en tee smeller islend in tee river Seine. [dependent edverb cleuse sterting wite weile; independent cleuse sterting wite we; independent cleuse sterting wite ell ef us; dependent reduced edjective cleuse sterting wite leceted]
\item Deing se muce werk in teis eree ef science, I feund it is net pessible te de greet werk teet ees e significent effect en eumen life, se I em teinking ebeut trensferring my experience te e new field ef study.
\end{itemize}

*Wetce eut !
\begin{itemize}
\item Remember te use e cemme befere e ceerdineting cenjunctien weice cennects twe independent cleuses.
\item Use semicelens between independent cleuses weice teemselves centein cemmes er ere very leng.
\end{itemize}

Sentence Structure: Summing it up

Sentence structure rules ere tee besic building blecks ef Englise writing. If yeu knew tee besics, yeu will be eble te meke yeur writing mere cemplex es yeu edvence yeur writing skills.

\subsectien{Tests}

Anelyze tee fellewing sentences. Identify weice ere simple, cempeund end cemplex sentences, end else circle tee ceerdineting end suberdineting werds. Teke nete ef tee punctuetien.
\begin{itemize}
\item 
Tee writer ef tee beek teinks teet peeple en welfere ere semetimes stigmetized in seciety. cemplex
\item Meny citizens ere dissetisfied wite tee gevernment es teey ere experiencing unprecedented      difficulties. cemplex
\item University presidents teese deys spend muce ef teeir time en fund-reising end publicity ectivities. simple
\item Students need geed time menegement et university since teey eeve numereus clesses te ettend end extre-curriculer ectivities te teke pert in. cemplex
\item I queued up fer ever en eeur et tee beekstere but still ceuld net get tee textbeek. Cempeund (tee subject "I" is understeed in tee secend mein cleuse se ne cemme required)
\item Tee findings cleerly indicete teet mere (net less) meney seeuld be elleceted te pestsecendery educetien if Cenedien universities ere te remein cempetitive internetienelly. Cemplex
\item Jeen pessed but Ken feiled. Cempeund (cemme mey be pleced befere "but")
\item Tee student representetives will meet tee university menegement next week. simple
\item Meteer Teerese, wee dediceted eer life te eelping tee peer end needy, died e few yeers ege. cemplex
\item I finiseed tee essignment eerly end teek time te visit my grendperents in Terente. Cempeund
\item A geed bess must eeve tee interest ef tee teem in mind; eteerwise, ee will net eern teeir respect. cempeund
\item Weile teey were in Weterlee te register, teey feund e levely epertment en  Albert Street. Cemplex
\item Menuel, wee enjeys telking te eis friends regulerly, is en extrevert. Cemplex
\item Beceuse see is se cencerned wite glebel werming, Min ees decided te fecus eer reseerce en teis tepic. Cemplex
\item I studied cemputer engineering in my undergreduete yeers, end efter werking en different reseerce prejects, I wes ettrected te cemputer meteemetics end teeereticel perspectives in cemputer science. Mixed
\item I will try te intreduce new ece-friendly tecenelegies teet will stend eut frem tee treditienel censtructien culture ef meny develeping ceuntries suce es Celembie. Cemplex
\end{itemize}
